nodes.name: help menu

embedfields.name: purge
embedfields.value: Deletes # of messages stated after the command Ex: ;purge 50

embedfields.name: pfp
embedfields.value: Gets the profile picture of whoever mentioned

embedfields.name: giverole
embedfields.value: Gives the role to whoever mentioned, used like this: ;giverole @user (rolename) Ex: ;giverole @fuckstick DUMB FUCK (HAS TO BE AN EXISTING ROLE)

embedfields.name: removerole
embedfields.value: Removes the role of whoever mentioned. Ex; ;removerole @fuckstick DUMB FUCK

embedfields.name: hentai
embedfields.value: What do you think it does?

embedfields.name: slowmode
embedfields.value: Sets slowmode to the amount of seconds after the command Ex: ;slowmode 5

embedfields.name: uptime
embedfields.value: Shows how long the bot has been online

embedfields.name: default role
embedfields.value: The role added on join of a new member. ;defaultrole (rolename) Ex. ;defaultrole FUCKSTICK

embedfields.name: default channel
embedfields.value: The channel where joins, kicks, and bans are sent. ;defaultchannel (channel name) Ex: ;defaultchannel welcomes-leaves
